</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[857,945,1251,1277]" pageId="108" pageNumber="109" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
from congenerics, see the identification key, and Differential diagnosis under 
<taxonomicName authority="Barkalov &amp; Ståhls, 2022" authorityName="Barkalov &amp; Ståhls" authorityYear="2022" box="[628,806,1286,1312]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Cheilosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="108" pageNumber="109" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="spinosa" status="sp. nov." subGenus="Cheilosia">
